    "Having concluded the ALDE-based evolutionary campaign with substrate 1a, we sought to understand the substrate scope of the sequences explored in this project.",
    "We screened eight styrene derivatives (1b-1i) for cyclopropanation using the sequences from Round 2 of ALDE (Fig.",
    "S50 of Supplementary Information).",
    "The variants show different yields for each of the substrates, even though some of these substrates differed from 1a only by a single atom.",
    "Nevertheless, for every substrate, nearly all of the Round 2 variants were higher yielding and more selective for their respective cisdiastereomers than the parent protein, ParLQ (Figs."
